      "@id": "https://doi.org/10.1093/bioinformatics/btag105"
    },
    "FishFeats: streamlined quantification of multimodal labeling at the single-cell level in 3D tissues"
  ],
  "http://schema.org/dateCreated": "2026-06-17T11:08:00+00:00",
  "http://schema.org/dateModified": "2026-06-17T11:23:29+00:00",
  "http://schema.org/description": "FishFeats: napari plugin to perform quantification of multimodal labeling at the single-cell level in 3D tissues.FishFeats allows to perform together in the same pipeline several analysis to quantify epithelia cells in 3D tissue, analysing cell morphology, nuclei, immuno-staining or RNA expression. The plugin allows flexibility to let the user choose the relevant step for a specific biological question. ",
